# **The Power of Your Perspective**

Your perspective makes your life run smoothly or sputter and stall. It’s the difference between getting stuck in a problem or finding a solution and creating breakthrough.

It's that powerful\!

Will you start the day out happy or grumpy? It depends on your perspective. Are you looking at the beautiful sunshine or the poop on the sidewalk? 

A lost client or sale or a sick child can be a setback or an advantage--*depending on your perspective.* Are you looking at the roses or the thorns in your life?

You cannot control other people's actions, but you can control your own.

And you can choose whether to rejoice in the roses or curse at the thorns. You can choose your perspective.

Maximizing your personal freedom means choosing the perspective you’re going to adopt in any given situation.

You have the freedom to let a few thorns sour your venture or to rejoice that a rose has finally bloomed.
